    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (((v0 + 0.05 + v1 + 0.36) / tmp) / (tmp * (tmp + 0.70 * v0 + 0.66)))
    v2 = v0
    v2 = ((wp.exp(v0 + 0.31) + v0) * wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.50)))
